## Latest implementation pass (2026-06-18)
- Applied remaining Weekend Planner hardening:
  - `apps/ti-web/app/_components/planner/PlannerClient.tsx`
    - Routed all manual event “Add event” entrypoints through `openManualEventFromTop()` so explorer/unverified cannot bypass gating via duplicate CTA.
    - Added `sanitizeIcsNotesForDisplay()` and applied sanitized ICS notes rendering for list cards.
    - Added inline whitespace-normalization helper used by notes rendering/path.
  - `apps/ti-web/app/_components/planner/PlannerCalendar.tsx`
    - Reworked month navigation in `goToAdjacentRange()` to jump to explicit month starts to avoid edge-date drift in Schedule-X.
