    - Added `sanitizeImportedNotes()` export.
    - Applied note sanitization inside `normalizeIcsEvents()` so imported ICS notes strip URLs and UUID-like tokens at ingestion time.
  - `apps/ti-web/lib/planner/ics-import.test.ts`
    - Added unit tests for sanitizer and unstructured ICS description privacy filtering.

